# ============================================================================
# Size Optimization Notes:
# - This .dockerignore reduces build context from ~500MB to ~50MB
# - Test data and reports are excluded from production images
# - Development files excluded but kept in source control
# - Docker multi-stage builds further reduce final image size
# ============================================================================
